40
00:01:37,679 --> 00:01:39,649
Plus hangars for fighter planes.

41
00:01:39,649 --> 00:01:41,310
Plus ammunition bunkers.

42
00:01:41,310 --> 00:01:44,079
And, sometime in the past month or so,

43
00:01:44,079 --> 00:01:46,689
