44
00:01:46,689 --> 00:01:48,479
This is the Fiery Cross Reef.

45
00:01:48,479 --> 00:01:52,200
It’s one of three fortified outposts China
has built,

46
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:54,219
including Subi Reef and Mischief Reef.

47
00:01:54,219 --> 00:01:56,840
They’re part of the Spratly Islands.

48
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:58,659
As you can see from this map,

49
00:01:58,659 --> 00:02:00,359
