54
00:02:08,289 --> 00:02:10,229
And according to their report,

55
00:02:10,229 --> 00:02:13,099
the Chinese regime has put some serious hardware

56
00:02:13,099 --> 00:02:14,620
on these islands.

57
00:02:14,620 --> 00:02:16,610
You know, for peace.

58
00:02:16,610 --> 00:02:18,450
It was that same drive for peace that lead

59
