islands,

77
00:03:06,019 --> 00:03:08,019
despite this 2002 agreement they signed with

78
00:03:08,019 --> 00:03:09,019
the Association of Southeast Asian Nations

79
00:03:09,019 --> 00:03:10,310
not to change any geographic features

80
00:03:10,310 --> 00:03:11,640
in the South China Sea.

81
00:03:11,640 --> 00:03:15,050
I mean, they probably forgot what they promised

82
00:03:15,050 --> 00:03:17,750
