84
00:03:19,900 --> 00:03:22,170
those made-made islands.

85
00:03:22,170 --> 00:03:23,640
And of course they completely ignored

86
00:03:23,640 --> 00:03:26,159
the 2016 ruling by the Hague,

87
00:03:26,159 --> 00:03:29,060
